author: @cc_faith
text: Onces, check out ONCEasONE_ on twitter for goals for Twice’s next comeback. Once fanbases on Twitter have worked together to set a goal of 40 million Youtube views in the first 24 hours. Whether you think it’s too high or low, please do your absolute best anyway since this will be Twice’s second full album and their 5th anniversary. Our fandom has grown and we have also become more united and stronger especially during Choeaedol voting. Remember to stream log-in, manually search the comeback title plus “twice” so it appears in more people’s searches, watch the video in at least 480p, do not pause or change speed, do not use incognito mode, do not mute, do not clear history and cache, no multiple tabs, do not loop the comeback song, don’t use playlists within the first 24 hours, watch 2-3 random videos between the comeback video. You could watch other Twice videos, cute animal videos, whatever you like just make sure you mix up these videos each time so it’s not considered bot behaviour so your views can get counted. Anyway please share this with all the onces you know, let’s work hard!

everyone talking about Mina LoL

Nayeon : those student who seem easygoing and like to have fun, but actually ace everything from academic, PE, and even arts

Momo : The rich kid who like to play and treat her friends
Sana : Those popular and famous girl at school. everyone knows her because she is kind, friendly, and admirable
Jihyo : the teacher's pet. her friends can count on her. and seems to be student council member
Mina : the quiet kid. seems distant at first, but when get to know her better, she's kind and warm
Dahyun : the one who lit up the atmosphere at class. including the teachers can laugh with her smart wit
Chaeyeong : likes to draw something at the back of her books. so creative especially when it comes to school events
Tzuyu : the pretty girl at school. everyone wants to be her friends, but too afraid to approach

that's the image that comes on my mind. just my imagination

author: @iya9990
text:
Twice as students

Tzuyu: the clueless student who asked for homework on their first day
Dahyun: the friendly student who notice everything
MoNabelle: the shy but not shy to open a store in the classroom
Sana: the 'talking' machine, also a harry potter student who just wants to study until dahyun and tzuyu came to her life. 
Mina: the cool foreigner student who pretends to be a human, she's actually a penguin who goes to school
Chaeyoung: the smol rapper student, she's in highschool but she's actually an elementary student
Nayeon: the famous unnie of the school, has the 101% confidence who always says that she's pretty but actually it's true
Jeongyeon: the student whose absent on her first day of school, but she's excuse, and I'm happy that she's doing well today. 

Mrs. Kang i mean Ms. Park: the smallest and cutest teacher in the world, she's not just a homeroom teacher she's also a vocal teacher if u wouldn't pass her exam you'll get kicked out ( her exam is to hit the high note).
